71
00:04:53,144 --> 00:04:54,561
Next.

72
00:04:59,441 --> 00:05:03,654
William Harris, Master Sergeant, U.S.
Army, retired.

73
00:05:03,695 --> 00:05:05,405
I ran an ad in the "Times"

74
00:05:05,447 --> 00:05:06,907
