for ages.

153
00:09:17,491 --> 00:09:20,285
It would be fine for you.

154
00:09:20,327 --> 00:09:22,538
Could have it
redecorated, I suppose.

155
00:09:24,498 --> 00:09:25,916
Ok, mother.

156
00:09:25,957 --> 00:09:27,918
You got yourself a tenant.

157
