for a change.

186
00:10:50,917 --> 00:10:53,170
I don't want those cars
on the lot by Saturday!

187
00:10:53,211 --> 00:10:55,380
Yes, sir.

188
00:10:57,799 --> 00:11:01,470
Oh, and, uh,
by the way, cold one,

189
00:11:01,512 --> 00:11:02,971
