225
00:12:45,657 --> 00:12:47,909
No, they haven't
called me in months,

226
00:12:47,951 --> 00:12:49,994
and they never will call me,

227
00:12:50,036 --> 00:12:52,247
nor will any studio
ever call me.

228
00:12:52,289 --> 00:12:55,875
