244
00:13:39,544 --> 00:13:40,962
And I'm all for you.

245
00:13:41,004 --> 00:13:42,589
You've got real integrity,

246
00:13:42,631 --> 00:13:45,843
artistic integrity,

247
00:13:45,884 --> 00:13:48,094
the only kind
that means anything.

248
00:13:50,305 --> 00:13:53,099
